title: Kenneth Cole Reaction Men's Watch Cases at Bed Bath & Beyond
transcripts: The watch case drawer holds up to 6 watches. It has watch forms to help watch bands keep their shape. There is a glass window lid to display watches and keep them clean and protected. The lower drawer has multiple compartments to hold keys, hufflings, money clips. The watch winder holds up to 6 watches. Electrically powered, it comes with an AC adapter and automatically winds kinetic watches. It has three different rotation modes and a glass lid to keep watches clean and protected. The Hudson watch case and watch winder by Kenneth Cole Reaction home are available exclusively online and at select Bed Bath and Beyond stores. Make sure to view the other items available at men's Hudson collection.
